                             Photo of MFD Award

   The California State Lands Commission's Marine Facilities Division has
   been presented the prestigious Legacy Award of 2001
   "In recognition of extraordinary efforts to prevent oil spills." In
   particular, the Commission was cited for developing the Safety
   Assessment of Management Systems, or "SAMS."
